      <title>受日本和中国经济低迷影响，丰田销量和产量停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/toyota-s-sales-output-plateau-as-slump-persists-in-japan-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上个月，丰田汽车公司的销量和产量趋于平稳，得益于日本国内长期低迷后海外市场略有反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/toyota-s-sales-output-plateau-as-slump-persists-in-japan-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 04:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
