      <title>加密货币支持者争相担任美国监管机构负责人，比特币价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/bitcoin-btc-gets-boost-as-crypto-supporters-vie-to-head-sec-cftc</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有迹象表明，加密货币友好型候选人可能会在唐纳德·特朗普的领导下影响美国金融规则，比特币因此继续攀升至 100,000 美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/bitcoin-btc-gets-boost-as-crypto-supporters-vie-to-head-sec-cftc</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 01:04:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>如果特朗普实施较温和的关税，亚洲债券将落后于新兴市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-bonds-to-trail-em-peers-if-trump-enacts-milder-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果唐纳德·特朗普的关税政策比人们担心的更为温和，新兴亚洲债券的价格将变得更加昂贵，其吸引力将低于全球同行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-28/asian-bonds-to-trail-em-peers-if-trump-enacts-milder-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Nov 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市领跌亚洲，债券上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，中国股市表现不及该地区，因为交易员们正在等待下个月重要经济会议前北京决策者发出进一步刺激措施的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Nov 2024 22:37:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
